parameters:
Mercenary Captain Gale: It's surprising that you defeated
General Atu. If you're interested in my request, go to the
Oros bulletin board.

Mercenary Captain Gale: I'm really grateful that you're
willing to take on this request.
Mercenary Captain Gale: Auto, come over here!

Mercenary Captain Gale: This is our new recruit, quite a
well-built physique, don't you think?
Clea: Yes, I think she is more than capable of fighting.

Mercenary Captain Gale: That's right... Can I have a little
sword fight with you?

Mercenary Captain Gale: You should understand why I made
this request.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Mercenary Captain Gale: Auto is a bundle of talent. I want
you to bring out his full potential.

Mercenary Captain Gale: It's an honor to meet a Dragon
Slayer. As someone who has sought strength, I respect you.

Clea: I fought dragons not for the sake of strength, but to
take a new step forward.

Mercenary Captain Gale: That kind of spirit is what we call
strength. This request is actually from Auto.

Mage Relm: Is that person again!? Didn't we resolve the
previous request!

Mercenary Captain Gale: I thought the same and let them
challenge the arena. At first, they went to a good place,
but after losing once, they became useless.

Thief Nora: I, I somehow understand. When you fail, it
feels like you can't succeed anymore.

Priestess Sophia: Is there a special reason why you're so
fixated on Auto-san?

Mercenary Captain Gale: His father was also a mercenary. He
died during a battle with bandits while transporting
crystals.

Mercenary Captain Gale: You're a fool, protecting me...
Training Auto to prevent him from dying is my way of
atonement.

Mercenary Captain Gale: Auto will never give up being a
mercenary because he admires his father... That's why having
a strong spirit is essential.

Clea: Understood, I will make sure to have a strong
spirit.
Mercenary Captain Gale: Please, guide him for me.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Mercenary Captain Gale: With an unwavering strong heart...
If we obtain that, Auto should be unbeatable by anyone.

Mercenary Captain Gale: Could you go to the arena
occasionally? I want you to see how much Auto has grown.

Mercenary Captain Gale: It seems that Auto is living as a
warrior in the arena. Not just me, but his father should be
happy about it too.
